data.title: Jenna Ortega Says It’s ‘Very Easy to Be Terrified’ of AI: ‘It Feels Like We’ve Opened Pandora’s Box,’ but ‘There’s Certain Things It’s Just Not Able to Replicate’
data.description: Jenna Ortega sounded off on artificial intelligence at the Marrakech Film Festival, saying "it's very easy to be terrified" of it.
data.author: Ellise Shafer,Elsa Keslassy
